				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Fist Murphy is being punished for stealing a purse full of coin from the evidence room. He's being made to stand on one leg as punishment. Fist Clover occasionally comes to check up on him. Murphy is mortified, sore, and wishes the punishment was over. Clover has sympathy for him but also thinks he was a big dumb idiot."
